item.description:
On the Season 2 Season Finale, we uncover a murder/cannibal/suicide plot then take a look at the controversial conspiracy "God Was Raped."

Patreon
https://www.patreon.com/user?u=18482113

MERCH STORE!!!
https://tinyurl.com/y8zam4o2

Two middle school girls decided to commit massacre at their school. Their goal: kill their classmates, drink their victims' blood, and eat the corpses. It was a shocking plan that came frightfully close to becoming a reality.

Then we look at the Iceberg Conspiracy "God Was Raped." What does this phrase mean and is there any Biblical proof of such an act taking place?
